name: Listened to 2022 Spanish Grand Prixview | Formula 1 Podcast | Grid Talk Ep. 195

content.html:
Welcome to Episode 195 of our Formula 1 podcast, Grid Talk, hosted by Tom Horrox! Today the Grid Talk team is here to preview all the talking points ahead of the FORMULA 1 PIRELLI GRAN PREMIO DE ESPAÑA 2022. In this episode joining Tom, we have Tom Downey and Sophia Richmond from Everything F1.
